    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is ambiguous indexing from a slicer and is not possible to detect. See the warning: http://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/advanced.html#using-slicers\n\nYou can do this:\n\n```\nOn [8]: df.loc[(slice(None), 'b', 'c'), :]\nOut[8]: \n         1    2\na b c  NaN  NaN\n\nIn [9]: idx = pd.IndexSlice\n\nIn [12]: df.loc[idx[:, 'b', 'c'], :]\nOut[12]: \n         1    2\na b c  NaN  NaN\n```\n"
  },
