    "body": "@toobaz Additional reason that this is confusing is that `df.loc['a', 'b', 'c']` is actually interpreted as `df.loc[('a', 'b', 'c'), :]` and `df.loc['a', 'b', :]` as `df.loc[('a', 'b'), :]`. That is the reason those do work\n"
